Like New Rambler W/Finished Basement Set On 30 Wooded Acres Featuring Creek & Pond, Beautiful Country Views & Abundant Wildlife! Just 20 Mi To Virginia or 30 to Hibbing.  Built 2001, 2912SF, 5BR/2+BTH, 2 stall attached garage, 2 stall detached garage, beautiful open yard w/creek flowing to pond at NE corner of property.  Custom kitchen w/sit around island open to spacious living, dining & large deck. 3 BR/2BTH on main flr including luxurious master w/private full bath. Finished basement has high ceilings, family/movie room w/surround sound & fireplace, 2 lg BRs, lots of storage & 3rd BTH ready to finish. New teak floors, raised panel solid wood doors.  2 stall detached garage w/wood stove converted to game room & sauna. Maint free ext, concrete approach & sidewalks, additional storage bldgs, small historic Finnish cabin, 4 wheeler trails throughout acreage.  Good internet service. Great country home! Ready to move in!

description: Recently sold: $127,000. This property is a perfect place for an outdoors person or family to relax in the Minnesota Northwoods! It includes 10 acres of primarily high ground land adjoining 1000s of acres of state land with access to the St. Louis River. The cabin includes over 700 sg ft of living space, including two bedrooms. There is a 26x33 garage, plus a 20x30 insulated garage/workshop. Explore the ATV trails on the property or nearby public land. There is great deer and grouse hunting, a tree fort for the kids and more blueberries and raspberries than you could ever pick! Canoe and fish the St. Louis River! In the winter, enjoy groomed Nordic ski trails, skating rink and sliding hill less than 1/2 mile away, then come back and enjoy your own sauna! This property has a 105 ft drilled well, indoor composting toilet, and is extremely low maintenance. It''s the perfect place to enjoy the peaceful outdoors, only 30 minutes from Virginia or Hibbing.
